      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; key input parameters documented and traceable to published sources.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties (density 1056 kg/m³, dynamic viscosity 3.5 cP), pump geometry dimensions, and operating condition inputs documented and traceable to FDA benchmark specifications and published literature. Formal model input uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. Nominal input values used throughout; parameter documentation sufficient for this risk level."
    },
