      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample characterization documented in source publication.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from FDA benchmark study (Morrison et al. 2018) using standardized FDA generic pump geometry manufactured to published tolerances. Sample characterization documented in source publication. Formal test sample assessment as a standalone credibility factor not required at MRL 2."
